-- Cadiz Wants to Expand Securities Unit Outside of South Africa, CEO Says
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-11-08T10:24:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-08/cadiz-wants-to-expand-securities-unit-outside-of-south-africa-ceo-says.html
Cadiz Holdings Ltd., a South African
money manager and stockbroker, wants to expand the distribution
of its securities business outside its home market, Chief
Executive Officer Ram Barkai said.  The company, based in Cape Town, also wants to introduce
new products to take the securities business to the “next
level,” he said in an interview broadcast by Johannesburg-based
CNBC Africa today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  